name: AR Treasurer
tweet: To sum it up, the salute “Slava Ukraini” emerged just over 100 years ago as an underground phrase of hope among Ukrainians symbolizing independence, freedom, and sovereignty. Today more than ever, the phrase represents their fight for democracy and independence.

name: AR Treasurer
tweet: Last week, Ukraine President Volodymr Zelenskyy addressed a joint session of Congress virtually. As I watched, I was taken by the phrase “Slava Ukraini,” or “Glory to Ukraine!” I took time to look it up and try to get a better understanding of its origins and history.  https://t.co/P5rh5U5oMC

tweet: Bottom line: Whether or not the bonds cater to ESG practices - promoting clean energy over fossil fuels, for example - should be up to the community issuing the bonds and NOT the federal government.   It's a slippery slope and I'm against it.

name: AR Treasurer

name: AR Treasurer
